Text.string: You defile this holy place, Vault Thief!
I can see the sin beneath your skin!
You should not have come here, heretic!
You will listen, AND you will DIE!
The Twin Gods are not to be questioned!
Your petty quest leads only to ruin!
The Firehawk is a pretender to the Siren throne!
Is that all you've got? Rrgh! Rrgh! Let's pump it up!
Hate the sin AND the sinner!
Your punishment has only just begun!
The Vaults belong... TO THE TWIN GODS!
The great God-Queen... WILL CONSUME YOU!
You cannot kill the word of the Gods!
I am protected by the divine!
I see it! The Great Vault!
